creator: Anna Katharine Green
description:
LibriVox recording of The Doctor, his Wife, and the Clock by Anna Katharine Green.
Read in English by Carolin Kaiser
A man has been shot dead in his house. Ebenezer Gryce is on the case, but he has no leads, no witnesses, no evidence -- until he decides to talk to the neighbors of the victim, a blind doctor and his beautiful wife.. - Summary by Carolin
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.

title: The Doctor, his Wife, and the Clock

reviews.reviewbody: So pleased to have another Anna Katharine Green story with the ubiquitous Gryce on the case!
